review.reviewBody: I tried the Seafood Fried Rice/ 明太子海皇炒飯 and the Braised Bean Curd & Eggplant with Salted Fish/ 漁香茄子滑 豆腐 this time and they're both AMAZING! I couldn't stop eating, it was so delicious! Well worth the price. Highly recommend!
The BBQ Duck was a little dry, but all dim sum was very good. Especially the Pan-Fried Eggplant Stuffed with Fish Paste in Black Bean Sauce/ 豉汁魚茸煎釀茄子 !!
Highest quality Chinese food in Vancouver
I have tried at least ten different dishes and they are all delicious! I highly recommend the sesame balls!
Wonton soup and the Conpoy and Crab soup all arrived hot and sealed perfectly. Great place to order dim sum or any meal!
